COMMONWEALTH JEWISH COUNCIL AND TRUST AWARD 
Mr. Mac Harb (Ottawa Centre, Lib.):
Mr. Speaker, I would like to pay tribute to this year's recipient of the Commonwealth Jewish Council and Trust Award.  
